revision.text: * [[File:Lanturn.png|35px]] Lanturn (attacking) vs [[File:Gyarados.png|35px]] Gyarados (defending) - Lanturn is dual electric-water typed and Gyarados is dual water-flying typed. Lanturn's electric type is 4x effective against Gyarados (2x for both water and electric) so this is the type that is used. Lanturn's attack against Gyarados is increased by a factor of 4 (4x) as per the type multiplier.
